                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Si leur frêle existence est promise au néant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Ne les sauvera pas du sort qui les attend.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Que sur moi, la satire épuise en paix sa rage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
