                    "line_text": "Mais qu’elle épargne au moins l’objet de mon amour !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Si j’ai semé du vent, j’affronterai l’orage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Mais sans livrer ta tête à la honte, à l’outrage,",
